sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant S as SimplifyService
    participant P as PaymentGateway
    participant G as GoldPartner
    U->>S: POST /api/v1/gold/purchase
    S->>G: GET /api/v1/gold-rate
    S->>P: POST /api/v1/pay
    P-->>S: payment success
    S->>G: POST /api/v1/allot-gold
    G-->>S: grams allocated
    S->>Mongo: persist tx and portfolio
    S-->>U: response

